==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Adventurer
<hw>Ad*ven"tur*er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>aventurier</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>One who adventures; <as>as, the merchant
<ex>adventurers</ex></as>; one who seeks his fortune in new and
hazardous or perilous enterprises.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A social pretender on the lookout for
advancement.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adventuresome</ent>⟦br⟧
